high_descs: Turn left walk forward then face the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Turn to your left then head to the table on your right
Put the knife in the mug
Pick up the mug with knife on the table
Turn right facing the black shelf
Put the mug with knife on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife on the shelf

high_descs: Turn left, proceed to sink on left.  Turn right to face sink.
Remove knife from sink, to the right of the spatula and below the sponge.
Turn left, proceed to table with toaster on it.
Place knife in cup to the right of the spoon.
Pick up cup with knife in it.
Turn right to face shelves.
Place cup on top shelf, to the right, between the two shakers.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife from the sink to a cup on a table, move both to a shelf.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up a knife
Go to the white table
Put the knife in a mug
Pick up the mug
Go to the small black table
Put the mug down on the black table
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on a small table
